  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Suddenly you wake up, dim lights and familiar corridors. Endless loop. The place is filthy. It's like this place is familiar, but it's worse than you remember. In this game you play as Jack Miller, wandering the corridors in an infinite loop, who knows, maybe later you'll find out why you're here and who you are.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678810/extras/e388b79fc7e7f2343c91085e6d0879bb.avif?t=1766357867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678810/extras_big/e388b79fc7e7f2343c91085e6d0879bb.avif?t=1766357867 width=800 height=596 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- A looping psychological horror experience</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Disturbing atmosphere and mind-bending illusions</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Subtle storytelling through environment and sound design</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Unsettling audio cues and eerie visual changes</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> - Prepare for 25 minutes of intense psychological horror</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Header & Main Capsule art :elenmayart</p>",
